org.codice.ddf.spatial.ogc.csw.catalog.common

Class CswSourceConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codice.ddf.spatial.ogc.csw.catalog.common.CswSourceConfiguration

  • public class CswSourceConfiguration
extends Object
    Domain object to encapsulate the configuration of an instance of a CswSource. CSW converters, readers, etc. will access this object to determine the latest configuration of the CswSource they are working on.
